Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.18,0:00:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ice Staff is so expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.47,0:00:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Most Things You Save, You End Up Never Using\NThe Ice Staff is so expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Most Things You Save, You End Up Never Using\NWe don't have this much money!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have this much money!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But without the Ice Staff,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't beat the boss of that cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's sort through what we have,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and sell what we can to get the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to sell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.89,0:00:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize we had so much stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were we keeping it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got too many herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And we never use holy water,\Nso there's no sense in keeping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Mirror Light, which we only\Never used to seal away the first enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have that thing?\NSell it or throw it away already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, for some reason,\Nwe just don't feel like throwing it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we try to sell it, they say,\N"You can't possibly sell this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:01:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We can start by selling\Nour old weapons and armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.41,0:01:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It fits perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess some people\Nreally like used bikini armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they want it for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a mystery why Mage's sold\Nfor the most money, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still not enough.\NWe need to sell more stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these?\NWe've got an awful lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, those are elixirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're near death, using one will\Nbring your HP and MP back to maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the ultimate medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But usually before things get that bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:01:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we heal little by little, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And since we never use them,\Nthey've piled up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's sell them all!\NWe'll never use them anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But if we ever need them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's never happened, which is why\Nwe have so many of them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We got enough money\Nto buy the Ice Staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's go fight that boss in the caves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss is behind that door...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I'm too tired to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anybody have an herb?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I just used our last one...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then, does anybody have a cure spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any MP left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we had an elixir...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What idiot convinced us to sell them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We sold all that stuff\Nto buy the Ice Staff,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can't fight like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll have to back out and try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's going to be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A treasure chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Come on, elixir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Or anything that can heal us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's an Ice Staff!